TITLE: Declaring a Koin Module in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a basic Koin module using the 'module' function. This is the foundation for declaring dependencies in Koin.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/definitions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
val myModule = module {
   // your dependencies here
}
```

