TITLE: Loading Properties from Default Location in Koin
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to load properties from the default koin.properties file at application startup. This enables configuration via property files.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/start-koin.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
startKoin {
    // Load properties from the default location
    // (i.e. `/src/main/resources/koin.properties`)
    fileProperties()
}
```

