TITLE: Initializing Koin in an Android Application
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to initialize Koin in an Android application by extending the Application class. This setup is required to use Koin with Android-specific features.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/setup/koin.md#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
class MainApplication : Application() {
    override fun onCreate() {
        super.onCreate()

        startKoin {
            modules(appModule)
        }
    }
}
```

