TITLE: Adding Koin Android Dependency in Gradle
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to add the Koin Android dependency to the project's Gradle file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/quickstart/android.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: groovy
