TITLE: Initializing Koin Container in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to initialize Koin with the startKoin function to create a container and load modules. This is the main entry point for setting up Koin in an application.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/start-koin.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
// start a KoinApplication in Global context
startKoin {
    // declare used modules
    modules(coffeeAppModule)
}
```

