TITLE: Initializing Koin in a Kotlin Application
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to start Koin in a standard Kotlin application. It demonstrates the minimal setup required to initialize the Koin dependency injection container with modules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/setup/why.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
