TITLE: Unloading Modules from Koin Container
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to unload modules from the Koin container, which releases their instances and definitions. This allows for dynamically removing functionality from the container.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/start-koin.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
unloadKoinModules(module1,module2 ...)
```

