TITLE: Registering Multiple Components in Koin Module
DESCRIPTION: Complete Koin module with both UserRepository and UserService registered as singletons, demonstrating dependency resolution with get().
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/quickstart/kotlin.md#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
val appModule = module {
     single<UserRepository> { UserRepositoryImpl() }
     single { UserService(get()) }
}
```

