TITLE: Starting Koin with Multiple Modules
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to initialize Koin with multiple modules. This is typically done at the start of an application to set up the dependency injection container.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/modules.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
// Start Koin with moduleA & moduleB
startKoin {
    modules(moduleA,moduleB)
}
```

