TITLE: Koin Android Context Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to configure Koin with Android context in the Application class.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-android/get-instances.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
class MainApplication : Application() {

    override fun onCreate() {
        super.onCreate()

        startKoin {
            // inject Android context
            androidContext(this@MainApplication)
            // ...
        }

    }
}
```

