TITLE: Installing Koin Plugin in Ktor Application
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to install the Koin plugin in a Ktor application. The snippet shows setting up Koin with a logger and specifying application modules to be used for dependency injection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-ktor/ktor.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
fun Application.main() {
    // Install Koin
    install(Koin) {
        slf4jLogger()
        modules(helloAppModule)
    }

}
```

