TITLE: Demonstrating Lazy and Eager Instance Retrieval
DESCRIPTION: Simple code example showing the difference between lazy evaluation using 'by inject()' and direct instance access using 'get()'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/koin-component.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
// is lazy evaluated
val myService : MyService by inject()

// retrieve directly the instance
val myService : MyService = get()
```

