TITLE: Adding UserViewModel to Koin Module with viewModelOf
DESCRIPTION: Extending the Koin module to include the UserViewModel using the viewModelOf function, which ensures proper lifecycle management of the ViewModel in Android.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/quickstart/android-viewmodel.md#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
val appModule = module {
    singleOf(::UserRepositoryImpl) { bind<UserRepository>() }
    viewModelOf(::UserViewModel)
}
```

