TITLE: Defining a Factory in Koin Module
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to declare a factory component using the 'factory' function. This provides a new instance each time the component is requested.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/definitions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
class Controller()

val myModule = module {

    // declare factory instance for Controller class
    factory { Controller() }
}
```

