TITLE: Eager Injection in Android Activity
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates eager dependency injection using the get() function in an Activity's onCreate method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-android/get-instances.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
override fun onCreate(savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState)

    // Retrieve a Presenter instance
    val presenter : Presenter = get()
}
```

