TITLE: Binding Interfaces in Koin Module
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to bind an interface to its implementation in a Koin module using the 'as' operator or generic type declaration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/definitions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
val myModule = module {

    // Will match type ServiceImp only
    single { ServiceImp() }

    // Will match type Service only
    single { ServiceImp() as Service }

}
```

