TITLE: Creating a TestApplication for Koin Dependency Overrides in Android Instrumented Tests
DESCRIPTION: Custom Application class that initializes Koin with both production and test modules. This approach allows overriding production modules in instrumented tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-android/instrumented-testing.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
