TITLE: Named Definitions in Koin Module
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to specify names for definitions to distinguish between multiple definitions of the same type in a Koin module.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/definitions.md#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
val myModule = module {
    single<Service>(named("default")) { ServiceImpl() }
    single<Service>(named("test")) { ServiceImpl() }
}

val service : Service by inject(qualifier = named("default"))
```

