TITLE: Implementing UserViewModel with Koin Dependency Injection
DESCRIPTION: ViewModel that depends on UserRepository, displaying a greeting message for a user if found. It shows how to use constructor injection with Koin.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/quickstart/cmp.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
class UserViewModel(private val repository: UserRepository) : ViewModel() {

    fun sayHello(name : String) : String{
        val foundUser = repository.findUser(name)
        val platform = getPlatform()
        return foundUser?.let { "Hello '$it' from ${platform.name}" } ?: "User '$name' not found!"
    }
}
```

