TITLE: Implementing UserViewModel with Repository Dependency
DESCRIPTION: Creation of a UserViewModel class that depends on UserRepository to display user information. The ViewModel extends Android's ViewModel class and provides a sayHello function to interact with the repository.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/quickstart/android-viewmodel.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: kotlin
