TITLE: Defining Android Components with Kotlin Classes
DESCRIPTION: Example classes showing different Android components including a service implementation, presenter, ViewModel, scoped session, and worker. Each class demonstrates different dependency injection scenarios.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-android/dsl-update.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: kotlin
