TITLE: Using Different Parameter Types in Koin (Kotlin)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases the usage of different parameter types in Koin, including 'parameterArrayOf' for indexed access, 'parameterSetOf' for type-based access, and 'parametersOf' for combined functionality. It demonstrates how to access values from these parameter collections.
