TITLE: Using Scope Component Extensions
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use scope component extensions for dependency resolution within a scoped component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/insertkoinio/koin/blob/main/docs/reference/koin-core/scopes.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
class A : KoinScopeComponent {
    override val scope: Scope by lazy { newScope(this) }

    // resolve B as inject
    val b : B by inject() // inject from scope

    // Resolve B
    fun doSomething(){
        val b = get<B>()
    }

    fun close(){
        scope.close() // don't forget to close current scope
    }
}
```

